.******************************************************************************
.* System         : ALL                                                       *
.*                                                                            *
.* Include Name   : DXPATCOD.PBL                                              *
.*                                                                            *
.* Function       : To Display a description from the PATCODFD file           *
.*                                                                            *
.* Author         : Justin Coates      11/02/1992                             *
.*                                                                            *
.* Variables req. : ATT       DIM       80                                    *
.* for DISPITEM     AFTDECP   FORM      2                                     *
.*                  AFTDECPF  FORM      2                                     *
.*                  BEFDECP   FORM      2                                     *
.*                  BEFDECPF  FORM      2                                     *
.*                  DECIMALP  INIT      "."                                   *
.*                  DIM2      DIM       2                                     *
.*                  FORM21    FORM      21                                    *
.*                  FORMAT21  FORM      21                                    *
.*                  LEFTBRAK  INIT      "("                                   *
.*                  LLCNT     FORM      5                                     *
.*                  SCRID     DIM       2                                     *
.*                  VAR       DIM       80                                    *
.*                  SP70      INIT      "                                   ":*
.*                                      "                                   " *
.*                                                                            *
.* Parameters     : SCRPSTFD record                                           *
.*                  TCODE         category for data                           *
.*                  ACODE         data value                                  * .*                                                                            *
.* Modifications  :                                                           *
.*        V9.02.01  05/09/2001  Greg Horvat      SRF 12679                    *
.*                  Changed to open patcodes before the read                  *
.*                  15/10/1992    Justin Coates  (HONG KONG changes)          *
.*                  changed to use DISPITEM (not dxsetval)                    *
.******************************************************************************
DXPATCOD  MOVE      SP20,TDESC              * clear description
          PACK      ACODE,ACODE,SP3
          MATCH     SP3,ACODE               * see if have a code
          IF        !@EQUAL
            OPEN      PATCODE1,"patcodes"
            MOVE      "Invalid Code",TDESC
            PACK      KEY5,TCODE,ACODE,SP10
            CALL      RDCODE1
          ENDIF
          PACK      VAR,TDESC,SP30,SP30,SP30
          CALL      DISPITEM                * display description
          RETURN
